        Document(
            page_content="A. Chrome\n1. Buka Chrome\n[Gambar: https://help.nusawork.com/storage/help/images/Y3dR6TQVvVVNelBXXd19NxfYbmpSGoCG6iVl0Vmg.png]\n\nLalu selanjutnya ikuti langkah berikut\n[Gambar: https://help.nusawork.com/storage/help/images/6aJhAIKIG6sAbxH75R0mj24xfbJfPqM28a3dzWOv.png]\n1.  Klik ikon tiga titik vertikal di pojok kanan atas\n2. Pilih \"Delete browsing data\"\n3. Pilih rentang waktunya (misalnya: \"All time\" untuk hapus semua)\n4. Di tab \"Basic\", centang opsi \"Cookies and other site data\"\n5. Klik tombol \"Clear data\"\n\nB. Safari \n1. Buka Safari\n[Gambar: https://help.nusawork.com/storage/help/images/GxvCJzVAntQYiutnMOAjY1WUGsNukpk85gbMlEvm.png]\nLalu selanjutnya ikuti langkah berikut\n[Gambar: https://help.nusawork.com/storage/help/images/EeeVWLev98lwZP4t2vBp1K94CxYdFEFDk0cIfLIs.png]\n1. Klik menu Safari (di pojok kiri atas)\n2. Pilih \"Settings\" atau \"Preferences\"\n3. Masuk ke tab Privacy\n4. Klik \"Manage Website Data...\"\nDi situ Anda bisa:\nKlik \"Remove All\" buat hapus semua cookies\nAtau pilih satu per satu situs, lalu klik \"Remove\"\n\n[Gambar: https://help.nusawork.com/storage/help/images/5PxBm5yAkQ1af62i9Z4tg5dQNYc4cK9E7nAIH4qR.png]\nTerakhir, klik Done lalu Remove Now",
            metadata={"id": 594, "title": "Cara Menghapus Cookies di Berbagai Perangkat", "url": "https://help.nusawork.com/cara-menghapus-cookies-di-berbagai-perangkat"},
        ),

        Document(
            page_content="Di Nusawork anda dapat memberikan feedback/ atau masukan tentang fitur-fitur nusawork, kami akan merespon feedback tersebut dengan beberapa status seperti dijelaskan berikut ini :		\n\n    \n        \n            Status\n            Keterangan\n        \n    \n    \n        \n            New\n            Feedback masih baru masuk dan belum di-review\n        \n        \n            Ignored\n            Feedback diabaikan karena tidak relevan\n        \n        \n            Noted\n            Feedback diterima, tapi ditampung dulu belum masuk ke daftar pengerjaan\n        \n        \n            Need Discussion\n            Feedback perlu didiskusikan karena bisa dari ketidakpahaman user maupun tidak dimengerti developer\n        \n        \n            Accepted\n            Feedback diterima, dan dimasukkan ke daftar pengerjaan tim\n        \n        \n            In Progress\n            Feedback sedang dikerjakan tim\n        \n        \n            Done\n            Feedback selesai dikerjakan tim dan telah dapat digunakan oleh User\n        \n    \n\nEnglish: \nFeedback Status Description\n\nAt Nusawork, you can provide feedback or suggestions about Nusawork's features. We will respond to your feedback with several statuses as explained below: \n\n    \n        \n            Status\n            Description\n        \n    \n    \n        \n            New\n            Feedback is newly submitted and has not been reviewed\n        \n        \n            Ignored\n            Feedback is ignored because it is irrelevant\n        \n        \n            Noted\n            Feedback is acknowledged but currently on hold and not added to the task list\n        \n        \n            Need Discussion\n            Feedback requires discussion, possibly due to user misunderstanding or unclear for developers\n        \n        \n            Accepted\n            Feedback is accepted and added to the team's task list\n        \n        \n            In Progress\n            Feedback is currently being worked on by the team\n        \n        \n            Done\n            Feedback has been completed by the team and is now available to users",
            metadata={"id": 595, "title": "Keterangan Status Feedback", "url": "https://help.nusawork.com/keterangan-status-feedback"},
        ),

